      "content": "That makes sense. It's the kind of thing that's super annoying because it's too small to trigger a major investigation, but it just keeps happening. \n\nIf we were to do a deeper dive into the \"process\" side of it, are there any other subtle technical or operational ways these tiny, unexplained shortages could be creeping into the system without anyone noticing?",
